Text: enymexK RegistrationOLEObj Date May Dear enymexSM user In a previous email we forwarded for your review an enymexSM registration information package This consisted of both the enymexSM System User Agreement and examples of clickon screens that users will view and complete and agree to when they first log on to the enymexSM system The enymexSM System User Agreement must be signed and returned to Robert A Dagistino Director of Customer Service New York Mercantile Exchange One North End Avenue New York NY In addition to the two documents previously sent enymexSM trading companies will be required to fill out a single Registration Form This form is now available on the enymexSM website by clicking on to How Do I Trade Getting Started Registration for enymexSM We request that you complete this registration form and submit it either on line or print out a copy and fax it to the clearing company you intend to use for the clearing of enymexSM trading and the New York Mercantile Exchange attention Robert A Dagistino at Any questions can be answered by contacting Robert A Dagistino via email at or via telephone at or if you wish you may contact our Customer Service Call Center toll free at enymexx or email to Thank you Sincerely Robert A Dagistino Director of Customer Service New York Mercantile Exchange
